
  * Add support for newer NVIDIA sensors.
    Requires libxnvctrl >= 256.25.
  * New mbmon plugin.
  * Make udisks plugin poll for new value.
  * Set icon name on dialog windows.
  * Several small cleanups and bugfixes.
  * Several help fixes.

